# Files in the working tree that should NOT be uploaded to Vercel.
#
# Why this exists: Vercel enforces a 100 MB per-file limit during deploy. The
# 188 MB AURA DEMO.mov sometimes lives in /public during local edits, but the
# real demo is now embedded from YouTube via DemoVideoModal.tsx, so the local
# copy is redundant and would block every deploy.
public/AURA DEMO.mov

# Local-only screenshots / scratch artifacts that shouldn't ship.
public/Screenshot*.png
